-dark:#C98A7D77\"> \"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">你的目标文件夹路径</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">structure </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> get_folder_structure_v2</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">root_dir</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"># 打印结果</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">import</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> pprint</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">pprint</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">pprint</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">structure</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div cla